Reasoning: The paper discusses the use of media-based modulation (MBM) in the uplink of a massive MIMO system, which involves communication theory (cs.IT) and communication networks (cs.COMM). The paper also discusses the potential performance advantage of multiuser MBM (MU-MBM), which involves multiple access (cs.SI) and networked systems (cs.NI). Additionally, the paper proposes an efficient MU-MBM signal detection scheme that uses compressive sensing based reconstruction algorithms, which involves multimedia (cs.MM).
